@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health check / Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Get all floors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/floors

### Register a person movement
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/person-movements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personId": "{{$guid}}",
  "x": 1.5,
  "y": 2.3
}

### Get a person movement by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/person-movements/{{$guid}}

### OpenAPI document
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json

### Scalar interactive API documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/scalar/v1
